comment: Cousins (NOP) does not obtain a legal guarding position and is inside the restricted area when the contact with Randle (LAL) occurs.
Moore (NOP) does not make contact with Russell (LAL) on the jump shot attempt.
Randle (LAL) sets the screen on Moore (NOP) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Holiday (NOP) maintains legal guarding position and Ingram (LAL) loses control of the ball.
Russell (LAL) commits a take foul on Cunningham (NOP).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a common foul is confirmed.
Moore (NOP) legally contests Russell's (LAL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Randle (LAL) makes body to body contact with Davis (NOP) that affects his SQBR.
Russell (LAL) commits a take foul on Moore (NOP).
